{"type":"message","id":"6b2b897c","parentId":"109bd594","timestamp":"2026-04-03T21:24:03.085Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Fri 2026-04-03 18:23 GMT-3] Leia C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\data\\006_pt\\o_quitandinha_ia_ser_o_maior_casino_do_mundo_-_o_brasil_proibiu_o_jogo_2_anos_depois_de_inaugurar\\b2\\sectors\\s3_visual_planning\\inputs\\s3_source_package.json e produza C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\data\\006_pt\\o_quitandinha_ia_ser_o_maior_casino_do_mundo_-_o_brasil_proibiu_o_jogo_2_anos_depois_de_inaugurar\\b2\\sectors\\s3_visual_planning\\operators\\symbolic_event_extractor\\output.json com contract_version s3.symbolic_event.output.v1. Extraia eventos simbólicos/ideacionais visuais relevantes. Use scene_ids e notas curtas. Salve o JSON e responda com o caminho."}],"timestamp":1775251443076}}
{"type":"message","id":"55b623fe","parentId":"6b2b897c","timestamp":"2026-04-03T21:24:07.308Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0b8b1c4da54ef2910169d02ff54fc48191aabd5f96282c0fd6\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp0C_3aHRK2VLHJ5o2gDZ_yVLJecXTRohJafAecPiRgfOpHU_VQO2LOYs-l_9M0-RjS8Piyg_KZ4uIY_Bdz35qNO9gvC5j-ApqQoOSqojXogt_yoNaFZj7lbIXms726cUplyWAzMKOF2iM6aZPB--hGhn8BXdHkinHxRUvrB0PLIIiYaSUMGwJE_9vBh3waiFpjUewHQzBwJGuODR-qkwYmr9o0I13eYA0TJl7p6Ne-pK6eEaYjukeUklZZUbM_xT29Do4viSkzhP5BnxOQ3bIwbz8a7SwW7k9HDhB5cZzWqbd9XdQNaKUUFrhjvAVaVvRb0DIhzRl1CVr2LDUpxoTLU8IxwA7b8ustokxLUI5CCAOtdoEHI2vMzJbRuyr5AJ-vrrZnaeSNs7ZFqeHjMNPn2ipTW-Zfk95rrIQa7DNVrwaICrgTRF1FQ2tT2xKmFGb4YqYZ2YvudhwVRgrTAfXaLP2m0MvBsk223b46Hl4iiWZ9yWdepBdxwHgodmzEOoZPRHH4K7eKOA7kIg2s9f0AUpGaOr-HSRHxdLHDvDtUFhi4lW6XMNhbLpDXtrIQUuXH2SeGJWyAq8ifZw4E-hxJeLXp2iVeHO5V22H0bIk9fJPDY-F_1uZGW3TYVx5Cu7CcEegJGyLIm3KIN4a8-cfNVH_0TQSby7o0SkqWmR29KBFyqRntsdw0a6i7VwgtykDP3B5IUsB_JYKwBw-3ri7NtT3cke2pvFAiM-JeMcKS-egc6icCuCmyrFKZD6SPTFAeMwT30GeRSun7g_LpvseGK6uf68ssthGgRVQ7qbyUb3-Ql0Gt_LtITIbhVCjaAKNt7oRFBP2w75YTH6lshshpftIdn5GjNHpdw67izwdrFrC-klJJaKLpU5BfndIuZ-oWdSQ2L0Yi8_vT86iGqdIWiwLxLRTUZrpWZ70_e5PLBl_K3FT7EsjW5_ySyXfetAutpbl392ZDJ5oU36VvuO0muz00WQKUkJ7W5PWJiWmJloRvtNKC0MAX3FYk4J47btDUMT3JbA1CvnK5HqITM57G8pY6-BprzIp90IUNWCekNjqwv7M80UJW2EAcrjzCEaztgrBgXibnlbyy4ErX56bug690sJ5HLWuGaZbhZK9Lx1mE--UgKYBvMO8W0RBXXVd8aCmOXW5VOlbAIw64i5mgJqMGIcAQfCKUoW0pXzIGPPbv-qTfc8AzP0csKn0tUX4dJ5fpCiSw_yTy2MbD8Q76Yv0fYwFqP2VyiJpJZmgY9iJ6KFhFGj45kypr7I8DJ8PXX4D8ep0Cf28o6zR3PG2xm14sGiCH7Nrpair2fVdrehPnqE-XPAs3z1cpi-Ya1nsPM8guZHgt4NP016xRxvKhDvRkZSsNOIdcUFYkw6IkFvMUvw_1ixAn0eaG5rLaMT6zzD6LnCpUOJMlDsH6YTPdBrnnaworDtH7TIOIFb9c0Hf04C2kPcagK-k-f_FTWvk8hXvMc-t4xZGsyWuiDB5jEIoikjUkIJEeqXxN0aQCDTaEOYUc0-dLU-YrZPNyXC_fBN71Bhqr2uKiJhABLl6EGn5-A==\",\"summary\":[]}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3SDcsaHw8b6iyiOWq4UpRhyt|fc_0b8b1c4da54ef2910169d02ff7b92481918b3fbbc6f3cc